{"tid":2413788,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子被控「大三罷」襲擊警長蔡華麟 罪名不成立","createTime":"2021-02-19T03:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T10:18:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c6be72cec275c7c39c83ff060b448fa58ba55a3f","tid":2413788,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:17:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13755&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69CJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=2518aec4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13755</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#崔美霞裁判官 #裁決<br />\n👤李(27)  #1111中環 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲擊警務人員<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月11日，在中環畢打街會德豐大廈外，襲擊執行職責的警長蔡華麟。 <br />\n<br />\n~裁決速報~<br />\n<br />\n法庭裁定被告罪名不成立🎉"},{"pid":"a8995e8e229854f8ee9508e35de6fbe17e27d75f","tid":2413788,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6309b16226de2b42dfaa1924cca2a78541b3af","tid":2413788,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:18:01.000Z","msg":"呀崔啲裁決一時時"},{"pid":"2bdb2aa1bee5629d5b9796fa7411420b61109bfd","tid":2413788,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets